name: pdfminer
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set version = "20191125" %}


package:
  name: pdfminer
  version: {{ version }}

source:
  url: https://pypi.io/packages/source/p/pdfminer/pdfminer-{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: 9e700bc731300ed5c8936343c1dd4529638184198e54e91dd2b59b64a755dc01

build:
  number: 1
  noarch: python
  script: "{{ PYTHON }} -m pip install . --no-deps -vv"

requirements:
  host:
    - python >=3.6
    - pip
  run:
    - python >=3.6
    - pycryptodome

test:
  imports:
    - pdfminer
  requires:
    - pip
  commands:
    - pip check

about:
  home: http://euske.github.io/pdfminer/index.html
  license: MIT
  license_file: LICENSE
  summary: 'PDF parser and analyzer'

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - pmlandwehr
    - nehaljwani
